latestPosts.caption:
As a stylist, it’s such a joy discovering and collaborating with young Indian brands - the creativity, the heart, the fresh perspective. 

These outtakes from a shoot with @three.clothing on a sunny afternoon reflect just that. I’m loving how homegrown talent is redefining fashion in such cool, thoughtful ways.

Photos by @angus.guite
